title: Switch Or How To Alter Your Ego 1974

sources.title: Switch Or How To Alter Your Ego 1974
sources.description: A shy, withdrawn female scientist invents a formula that turns her into a horny, oversexed nymphomaniac. Rather poor copy of the film with burned in subtitles in Danish, maybe. Lots of early porn stars and softcore actors in this one including Kathie Fitch which is apparently the real name of Chris Jordan.
